.TH DELPHI-ZINE 1  "delphitools-cli 0.1.0" "delphitools manual"
.SH NAME
zine \- Impose images into a single\-sheet folded\-zine layout (mini\-8 or accordion)
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBzine\fR [\fB\-\-fold\fR] [\fB\-\-panels\fR] [\fB\-\-double\fR] [\fB\-\-paper\fR] [\fB\-\-dpi\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] [\fIIMAGES\fR] 
.SH DESCRIPTION
Impose images into a single\-sheet folded\-zine layout (mini\-8 or accordion)
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-fold\fR \fI<FOLD>\fR [default: mini8]
Fold template: mini8 (classic 8\-page) or accordion (concertina)
.TP
\fB\-\-panels\fR \fI<PANELS>\fR [default: 8]
Panels for the accordion fold (4, 6, or 8). Ignored for mini8
.TP
\fB\-\-double\fR
Accordion double\-sided (front pages 1..N, back N+1..2N; flip on short edge)
.TP
\fB\-\-paper\fR \fI<PAPER>\fR [default: a4]
Output paper size (default: A4)
.TP
\fB\-\-dpi\fR \fI<DPI>\fR [default: 300]
DPI for raster placement (default: 300)
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
.TP
[\fIIMAGES\fR]
Page images in reading order. Count must match the fold: mini8 = 8; accordion = panels (single\-sided) or 2×panels (\-\-double)
